JIPSY - IPv6 for Java (Java IP version Six readY)

The software contained in this distribution is a drop-in replacement for the
parts of the java.net class package that are IPv4 dependent. The replacement
enables existing Java applications to utilise both IPv4 and IPv6 without
modification or recompilation.

The software is licensed under the GNU LGPL. Please see the file COPYING that came with this distribution for details.

See the file INSTALL for information on compiling and using this software.

The latest version of the software can be downloaded from:

http://www.progsoc.uts.edu.au/~mpf/jipsy

You can contact the author by email at:

mpf@uts.edu.au

